data.description: This is a wonderful home in a perfect location in Wichita Falls that is convenient to all the dining and entertainment!  This 3 bedroom 2 bath university park home has been renovated and made into a charming place to call home.  The outside of the house has been recently painted and a new roof was installed in 2023.  Inside the front door, you will notice beautiful hard wood floors, a nice sized living area with big windows for natural light, and a very spacious kitchen.  The main bathroom has been updated with new ceramic tile, new vanity and countertops!  The home offers 3 good sized bedrooms and the master has an updated bathroom.  The home has a spacious back yard perfect for weekend cookouts and it backs up to a city park which is great for the kids! Act quick on this one because it won't last long!
